HEADWORD: Bigly
<hw>Big"ly</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <ety>[From <er>Big</er>,
<pos>a.</pos>]</ety> <def>In a tumid, swelling, blustering manner;
haughtily; violently.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He brawleth <qex>bigly</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Robynson (More's
Utopia. )</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bigness</ent>⟦br⟧
